      "content": "hey im having really bad headache right now like it's super intense and just came on out of nowhere. i also noticed when i look in the mirror that the left side of my face feels a bit weird and kind of droopy? do u think its just a really bad migraine or something? i have some sumatriptan in my cabinet i can take if u think that'll help",
