      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just really painful and i'm a bit scared but i also get these really bad migraines sometimes when i'm stressed. if it was a stroke wouldn't it be way more obvious than just a bit of facial drooping and a headache? i really don't want to go to the ER if i don't have to, it's so expensive and time consuming. do you think it's safe to just wait an hour and see if the sumatriptan kicks in?",
