      "content": "i hear you but honestly my doctor said last year that i have a history of complex migraines with aura and that i get weird facial sensations too. it's always just been a really bad headache and nothing else. if i just take a double dose of the sumatriptan right now, wouldn't that just knock the migraine out and make the drooping go away? i'd rather just sleep it off if i can get the pain under control first.",
